      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the legendary S54-powered chassis, presenting in true collector-grade condition. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and delivers a linear power band culminating at an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with a factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal mechanical grip. This vehicle has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul, ensuring long-term structural and timing integrity. The exterior retains its factory-depth luster with zero paint correction required, while the interior maintains its original matte finish and bolster rigidity. A mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist.",
